Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:10.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:40.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Burning with rage toward humans, the Magic \NKnights who reincarnated as elves attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:45.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the others headed toward \Nthe royal capital to stop them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:47.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and encountered Rades, Valtos, and Sally,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:52.49,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,who had been sacrificed in order to \Nreincarnate the elves, and almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:57.53,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You guys piss me off, too, but right now,\N I want to kill that bastard Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:00.45,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The three former Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun members
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.12,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,joined them, and they \Nall hurried to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.58,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at the royal capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:08.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,To save her brother Nozel \Nand protect the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:11.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle awakened a new spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:13.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.31,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:19.10,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As for Finral...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:28.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Fallen Angel's Wingbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:33.82,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This is... my last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:37.86,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Your big brother's pretty confident \Nwhen it comes to agility and accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:40.79,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:42.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:44.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.70,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He finally stopped his younger brother\N Langris's destructive rampage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,which began when Langris\N reincarnated as an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.14,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But now, Patry, who had \Nreturned to the hideout,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:57.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,was about to set a \Nterrifying plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.21,main,patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Now all we have to do is fit the final
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.21,0:02:02.70,main,patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,magic stone into the pedestal in the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:06.48,main,patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,and activate the spell that \Nuses the entire kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:09.28,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wipe out all of the humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:13.30,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll take back this world, \Nmaking it a peaceful world for elves alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:15.99,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:20.99,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as those two wake up, \Nwe'll have all the actors in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.70,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Raging Bull\N Joins the Showdown!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:09.14,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. How do you feel \Nafter that long nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fana? Vetto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.48,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember your previous incarnations?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:18.25,top,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We were the Third Eye, weren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:20.50,sign_6102_39_Vetto_the_Despai,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(775,783)}Vetto the Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:20.50,sign_6102_40_Fana_the_Hateful,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(775,783)}Fana the Hateful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.43,top,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Fana the Hateful, Vetto the Despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:25.99,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,and Raia the Disloyal, was it? How hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto and Fana were previously part \Nof the Eye of the Midnight Sun's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.41,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,elite three, known as the Third Eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.37,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,where they fought against Asta and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:38.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto lost his life, and Fana's soul \Nleft the body it had inhabited,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:43.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,allowing that body to start a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:47.66,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Raia incubated the general traits of \Nthe human bodies they had inhabited
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:51.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and prepared new bodies \Nfor their souls to inhabit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.80,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.17,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're short on time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:59.62,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I could only incubate your bodies long \Nenough for you to be about fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:02.61,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're smaller than me, Vetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:06.06,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've died twice now. \NI can't exactly be picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:06.86,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:11.10,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Creating duplicate bodies \Nwith the exact same mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:16.58,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I've really gotta hand it to Sally \Nand her research on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:20.05,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad she's probably dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.34,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is much clearer this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.82,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,We used the evil eye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:32.26,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,to force your previous incarnation, \Nso your malice was probably stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.97,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Evil eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:42.50,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,True, I did feel half-asleep last time...\N like I was having a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:43.98,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.22,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,No response.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.53,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Salamander's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:56.07,italics,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,So someone else who was qualified \Nshowed up while Fana's soul was away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:06:01.16,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're strong enough right now,\N even without Salamander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:05.59,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you're right. If nothing else, \Nthere's no way I'd lose to those stupid humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.73,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm gonna take \Nyou to the Grimoire Tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.84,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,so hurry up and let one pick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:14.35,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, before that, we need some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.83,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.86,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}do{\i0} seem a bit bigger than they \Nwere the last time you were fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:39.42,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Soon this false royal capital created \Nby the humans will be no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.54,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,It appears they've finally gathered up above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.52,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.89,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,they must've received the revelation \Nin preparation for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:53.06,top,All,0000,0000,0000,,Those who guide the elves... \NThe Apostles of Sephira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:55.31,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(968,1)}The Apostles of Sephira
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.61,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:12.61,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,He may seem like that right now, \Nbut I'm certain Licht is actually in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:17.63,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Once the reincarnation is fully complete,\N he'll be back to the same old Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.55,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.12,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where's that one boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.59,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the weird thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:29.63,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,He was reincarnated, but somehow, \Nhis personality was still the human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.34,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:35.61,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He'll be with us \Nonce everything is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.58,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go wait over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:38.85,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:45.75,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Man, look at this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.82,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,The party's in full swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.82,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.96,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,By infusing Gravito Stones with magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.38,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,we will open the door to the underworld
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.33,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,that was sealed under Clover Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.88,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel, the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.35,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:24.73,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic space that acts as the \Nborder between this world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:28.00,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,The elves of antiquity entrusted it \Nto the humans in an ancient pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.36,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the Shadow Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.57,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Only the Apostles of Sephira, \Nten elves who are able
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.51,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,to receive divine revelations, can open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.37,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:41.97,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,When we put the final magic stone \Nin its pedestal inside the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:45.62,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,the elves' reincarnation \Nwill be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:49.00,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, the souls of the \Nhumans who owned these bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.97,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,will be sent to the underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:58.73,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,And because I am so beautiful... \NI shall not allow that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.83,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,David's dice magic acquires effects
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.17,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,that give him an advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.48,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,depending on his roll.\N Better rolls mean more advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:14.02,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,But getting this much power from a two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.49,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:20.58,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it probably won't do you \Nmuch good, but give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.00,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:30.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, there's a magical \Nspace spreading over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:35.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the hell's over there,\N but this looks pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.34,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we head on over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.35,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We will not let you get in the \Nway of the Apostles of Sephira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:49.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they're not just \Ngonna let us go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.39,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.36,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slash you all up!
