Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.36,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,but they've always been a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:49.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They're our teammates, the other Black Bulls!
