Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.31,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense the magic of the vanished pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.86,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,but they don't exist anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:33.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa... and Magna and Luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and Miz Charmy and Sally... are all gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.18,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:40.46,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The moment Captain Dorothy's \Nmagic activates, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.14,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Its targets are taken to the World of Dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.88,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,and there's not a thing they can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.25,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The World of Dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:52.12,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Now the cornerstone of their defense is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:54.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we should wrap things up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:03.52,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Combo Spell: Storm of Light Swords\N of Imperial Conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.44,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Licht!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:15.80,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,G-G-G-G-Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.28,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:20.58,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Curse Magic: \NDwelling of the Poison Cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea, Gordon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:29.63,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Conversion Magic: Poison to Cotton!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved! Thanks, Miz Grey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:39.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to kill us, Gordon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.35,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that was teamwork, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.94,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead with your precious Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.29,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.85,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Droit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.63,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.20,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Valtos, open up a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, those jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:09.79,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:16.56,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Get... away... from... me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:18.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.67,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he left the Raging Black Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:24.06,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And without Miz Charmy here, \Nthe others can't recover their mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.61,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No... My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:35.93,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,That was one hell of a spell, \Nand it doesn't look like
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:39.13,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,your body can keep up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:43.12,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't have much magic \Nleft right now, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.55,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.21,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, \NShriveled Little Mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't looking too good over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:52.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't just let Licht go like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:57.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you dumbasses can handle this!\N Surpass your damn limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.51,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, beanpole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:08.02,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Who died and made you boss, meathead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:11.60,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, some of them left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.19,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Then we need to quickly \Nkill the ones that are here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,so we can hurry after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.56,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Now... it's time for hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Find all of them, Eclat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.04,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:25.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Willpower's not gonna help you now, humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.61,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:38.80,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:41.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.80,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Eye Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:46.14,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Combo Spell: Reflect Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:49.53,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.31,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.27,italics,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.82,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,...move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.54,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:18:59.90,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,...my magic's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:05.93,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Eclat's magic allows her to immobilize \Nanyone who looks into her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.29,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It binds them physically, \Nbut also blocks their magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:12.79,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marie doesn't even have her grimoire yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.30,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's awesome, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:20.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can just die, completely helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.11,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.81,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not... yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:31.31,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:37.33,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn Gauche \Nand Marie back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:38.82,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:41.82,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,stop you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.83,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,My body can move again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:55.34,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,He nullified the magical effects?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:59.17,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Can all three of you move now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.01,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That's Licht's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.27,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Demon-Destroyer Sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:12.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That weapon's too good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.29,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Die and give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.97,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use transformation magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.02,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.04,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,...to make more mirrors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:25.53,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Magic: Forbidden Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:41.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's more powerful... \NI know Gauche's magic really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:44.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, he kind of pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:48.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Always attacking me unfairly \Nwith those weird beams...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't actually changed much \Nafter getting his body taken over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:56.60,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... And when he comes back, \Nhe'll insult us even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:21:00.37,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,And he'll keep showing us \Nthe photo of his little sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:04.86,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,and making figures of his little sister,\N and always having nose bleeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:10.12,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,He's... very... creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.29,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get him back to normal,\N even if it hurts us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.04,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,so we can complain directly to his face!
