Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:56.62,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:01.06,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,973)}Revival
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:22:59.91,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Revival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:04.11,sign_33090_345_Part_1_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(988,1)}Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:03.11,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Part 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:14.37,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are smaller now, \Nsince we didn't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:19.22,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I definitely jumped the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:22.88,sign_33090_345_Part_1_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:21.90,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Part 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:27.13,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I had a little too much time on my hands,\N so I incubated them too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:30.97,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto and Fana are way older now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:37.34,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I definitely took too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.35,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,My best friend, Gauche Adlai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:44.74,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Your little sister is basically my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:47.15,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Marie is my actual little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:51.20,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, \NPage 111: "The Eyes in the Mirror."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:54.12,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 111\N\N{\fs18} The Eyes in the Mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:54.12,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, little sister, I cry for you.
